The paper deals with geolocation inference on social media data, specifically on Reddit. This suggests that the paper could fall under the sub-categories of Social and Information Retrieval (cs.SI), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), and Social and Information Networks (cs.SOC). Additionally, the paper involves the use of text-based heuristics and machine learning models, which could also place it under the sub-categories of Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Cybersecurity (cs.CYBER).
